title: American Architects - A Survey of Award-Winning Contemporaries
description:
American Architects, A Survey of Award-Winning Contemporaries and Their Notable Works
Facts on File | 1989 | 0816014205 | English | 312 pages | PDF | 41 MB

A detailed survey of the leading exponents of contemporary American architecture, this reference guide examines the lives and work of more than 1000 architects. The text has been organized alphabetically and each entry lists biographical details and architectural achievements. The fully illustrated text has been indexed and cross-referenced by company, specialization and geographic location
